+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Fvs1Lo6qhE2hERG3kNUSPf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01VRoqda7WTvnHSfaG5ziUDs","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-07-permission-maze-design.md","content":"# Permission Maze - Document Management API Design\n\n## Architecture\n\nSingle Express app exported via `createApp()` from `src/app.ts`. Modular structure:\n\n```\nsrc/\n  app.ts          - createApp(), middleware setup, route mounting\n  routes/\n    auth.ts       - POST /auth/register, POST /auth/login\n    folders.ts    - CRUD /folders\n    documents.ts  - CRUD /documents\n    sharing.ts    - POST /documents/:id/share, POST /folders/:id/share\n    activity.ts   - GET /activity\n  middleware/\n    auth.ts       - Bearer token extraction and validation\n  store.ts        - In-memory data store (Maps)\n  types.ts        - TypeScript interfaces\n```\n\n## Data Model\n\n- **User**: id, username, passwordHash (plain for simplicity), createdAt\n- **Folder**: id, name, parentId (nullable), ownerId, createdAt, updatedAt\n- **Document**: id, title, content, folderId, ownerId, createdAt, updatedAt\n- **Permission**: id, resourceType ('folder'|'document'), resourceId, userId, role ('viewer'|'editor'|'owner')\n- **ActivityLog**: id, action, userId, resourceType, resourceId, timestamp, details\n- **Token store**: Map<token, userId>\n\n## Permission Resolution\n\n1. Check direct permissions on the resource\n2. If resource is a document, check permissions on its parent folder (and ancestors)\n3. Take the most permissive role found across all paths\n4. Role hierarchy: owner > editor > viewer\n\n## API Endpoints\n\n- `POST /auth/register` - body: {username, password} → 201 {user}\n- `POST /auth/login` - body: {username, password} → 200 {token}\n- `POST /folders` - body: {name, parentId?} → 201 {folder}\n- `GET /folders/:id` → 200 {folder, children, documents}\n- `PUT /folders/:id` - body: {name} → 200 {folder}\n- `DELETE /folders/:id` → 204\n- `POST /documents` - body: {title, content, folderId} → 201 {document}\n- `GET /documents/:id` → 200 {document}\n- `PUT /documents/:id` - body: {title?, content?} → 200 {document}\n- `DELETE /documents/:id` → 204\n- `POST /folders/:id/share` - body: {userId, role} → 200\n- `POST /documents/:id/share` - body: {userId, role} → 200\n- `GET /activity` → 200 [{log entries}]\n\n## Testing\n\nIntegration tests with supertest covering: auth flow, CRUD operations, permission checks, permission inheritance, activity logging.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":515,"cache_read_input_tokens":23167,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":515},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7cccab6c-6eb7-4896-8d8c-f45c0c7d18df","uuid":"7ec72bfa-6726-4690-8e93-177f1456b923"}
