assword} → 200 {token}\n- `POST /folders` - body: {name, parentId?} → 201 {folder}\n- `GET /folders/:id` → 200 {folder, children, documents}\n- `PUT /folders/:id` - body: {name} → 200 {folder}\n- `DELETE /folders/:id` → 204\n- `POST /documents` - body: {title, content, folderId} → 201 {document}\n- `GET /documents/:id` → 200 {document}\n- `PUT /documents/:id` - body: {title?, content?} → 200 {document}\n- `DELETE /documents/:id` → 204\n- `POST /folders/:id/share` - body: {userId, role} → 200\n- `POST /documents/:id/share` - body: {userId, role} → 200\n- `GET /activity` → 200 [{log entries}]\n\n## Testing\n\nIntegration tests with supertest covering: auth flow, CRUD operations, permission checks, permission inheritance, activity logging.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
